com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.provider

Class SymbolListItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.provider.SymbolListItems

  • public class SymbolListItems
extends java.lang.Object
    Storage class for managing symbol list items. This handles the generation of example symbol lists, and shows how to encode it. Provides methods for managing the list, and a method for encoding a symbol list message and payload.

        Parameters:

        itemInfo - - The item information

        isStreaming - - Flag for streaming or snapshot
        serviceId - - The service id of the market price response
        dictionary - - The dictionary used for encoding
        responseType - - The type of response to be encoded: refresh, add update, or delete update
